  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What I want to mention-- maybe it's not clear-- that I was in Ravensbruck Camp a short time, but I was sent in Ravensbruck working camp because-- I presume because I was a live prisoner of concentration camp, they sent me to work.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that where is the most of the time up to my liberation, I was in working camp, which is sent by Ravensbruck Camp.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wouldn't know exactly how close.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It might be not that close because I remember that was big, big factories [POINTING] on a place that nothing around it, just factories, you know.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The man factories was a few kilometers from women, because where I was working was only woman's working camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was men's, which was a few kilometers from there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And nothing was around us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The only surround us a very high voltage of wire, and that's that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were every morning escorted by SS men to the hall where we work and escorted back to where, where, quarter where we sleep, stay.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that this period was up to my liberation, working underground, having this appells, and this staying in the snow.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And all those nightmares was in working camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we were working day, and we were, we were working night, because they can take us at night and put us outside to stay while-- when they feel like us not to rest.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What were the sanitary facilities like?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Didn't I tell you that we-- our leisure time was spent knocking the lice.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
